import { Offcanvas } from "bootstrap"

const CartItem = () => {



    return ( <Offcanvas show={true} onHide={cartClose} placement='end'>
        <Offcanvas.Header closeButton>
            <Offcanvas.Title>Cart</Offcanvas.Title>
        </Offcanvas.Header>
    </Offcanvas> )
}
export default CartItem
